Package: predicter
Title: A Tool to Estimates the Time Needed to Conduct a Systematic Review or Systematic Map
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Neal", "Haddaway", email = "neal_haddaway@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to calculate the volume of evidence moving through the 
  process of a systematic review or systematic map, along with the time necessary to complete these
  steps. Default data are based on an empirical study by Haddaway and Westgate (2019) 
  https://doi.org/10.1111/cobi.13231.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: 
    tidyr
